data.description: Welcome to Antioch Estates of South Crestview! This brick home with new roof (10/2023) is conveniently located, and ready for you to make it yours. Spacious floorplan with primary suite on one side of the house and 3 bedrooms on the other side of the living area and kitchen. Dine overlooking your backyard with no neighbors behind! The dining room could be utilized as an office or playroom. Oversized primary suite with separate tub and shower, large double marble vanity, and a walk-in closet. Interior laundry room leads to garage with pull-down stairs for attic storage. Upgraded 2 x 6 rafters, attic fan automatically turns on at 90 degrees, 2022 Water Heater, HVAC 2014, and a washer and dryer included! Seller is willing to offer a $3,000 buyer credit/carpet or flooring allowance.
